  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The DES-OSA Score and the STOP-BANG score were predictive scores for Obstructive Sleep Apnea.

      This study will compare, among patients scheduled for bariatric surgery, these two scores as
      predictive scores for a difficult intubation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The DES-OSA Score and the STOP-BANG score were predictive scores for Obstructive Sleep Apnea.

      This study will compare, among patients scheduled for bariatric surgery, these two scores as
      predictive scores for a difficult mask ventilation of tracheal intubation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
